Package angstd.ui.views.view.export

Interface Summary
ImageExporter Interface ImageExporter defines all methods which are needed to export views in various formats.
 

Class Summary
DefaultImageExporter DefaultImageExporter is the basic implementation for the ImageExporter interface allowing the export in PNG, BMP and JPG format.
PDFImageExporter Class PDFImageExporter exports an image in PDF format using the open source iText library which is published under the NPL and LGPL license.
SVGImageExporter Class SVGImageExporter exports an image in SVG format using the open source batik library which is published under the Apache license.
 

Enum Summary
GraphicFormats Enumeration GraphicFormats defines all supported formats for exporting a view.
